            "title": "蘋果據悉籌備首款觸控螢幕Mac電腦 最早或於2026年底亮相",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"MacBook Pro\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Gf_DXpDGIB5UEb9BC8r3yQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/ab505bc5c1fd9809d62fb9cf4ab56f43\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"><span>MacBook Pro</span></figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 蘋果公司正準備推出觸屏版Mac電腦，標志著這家科技巨頭將扭轉聯合創始人史蒂夫·喬布斯時代以來堅持的立場。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士透露，蘋果計畫在2026年底或2027年初推出配備觸控螢幕的升級版MacBook Pro。代號為K114和K116的新機將採用更輕薄的機身設計，並搭載M6系列晶片。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此舉意味著蘋果將效仿其他電腦廠商的做法，整個行業在十多年前就開始推出觸屏版筆記型電腦。蘋果耗費數年時間制定其市場策略，旨在改進現有設計。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-95b8ec83-e285-365b-b80b-4e1cf9dbfc58-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博新聞社在2023年1月首次報導稱，蘋果在研發觸屏版MacBook Pro。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">因討論未公開消息而要求匿名的知情人士表示，新款筆記本將配備OLED顯示屏，與iPhone和iPad Pro採用的標準相同。這將是蘋果首次在Mac產品中採用這種更高端、更輕薄的顯示系統。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">蘋果的發言人拒絕置評。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"MacBook Pro攝影師：Samsul Said/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/x.lcLj865mWrenAhmOWaZw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/046b5da1b25be774dec0f2c040ababc0\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">MacBook Pro攝影師：Samsul Said/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Apple to Finally Enter Touch PC Market With MacBook Pro Revamp</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E7%B1%8C%E5%82%99%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%BE%E8%A7%B8%E6%8E%A7%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95mac%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6-%E6%9C%80%E6%97%A9%E6%88%96%E6%96%BC2026%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%95%E4%BA%AE%E7%9B%B8-192952582.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-17 06:00:46",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "泡泡瑪特獲看好 目標320元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"泡泡瑪特獲看好 目標320元\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/TnGfoziGKwU20aPDjlBBQg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-10/07a0ae20-aaec-11f0-bf7a-03059f4b9d8e\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">泡泡瑪特獲看好 目標320元</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
